%% QGX LMS - UML Activity Diagram / Flow Chart (Mermaid)
%% Core workflow: authentication, role-based navigation, protected actions, and auditing
flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Open QGX Application]
    B --> C{Has Active Session?}

    C -->|No| D[Show Login Page]
    D --> E[Enter Email and Password]
    E --> F{Credentials Valid?}
    F -->|No| G[Show Authentication Error]
    G --> D
    F -->|Yes| H[Create Secure Session]

    C -->|Yes| I[Load Session Context]
    H --> I

    I --> J[Fetch User Profile and Role]
    J --> K{Determine Role}

    K -->|Admin| L[Route to Admin Dashboard]
    K -->|Teacher| M[Route to Teacher Dashboard]
    K -->|Student| N[Route to Student Dashboard]
    K -->|Parent| O[Route to Parent Dashboard]

    L --> P[User Initiates Protected Action]
    M --> P
    N --> P
    O --> P

    P --> Q[Validate Request Payload]
    Q --> R{Payload Valid?}
    R -->|No| S[Return Validation Error]
    S --> T[Display Error Message]

    R -->|Yes| U[Check Role Authorization]
    U --> V{Authorized?}
    V -->|No| W[Return 403 Forbidden]
    W --> T

    V -->|Yes| X[Execute Business Logic]
    X --> Y[Read/Write Data in Supabase]
    Y --> Z[Record Activity Log]
    Z --> AA[Send Success Response]
    AA --> AB[Update UI / Notification]

    T --> AC{Retry Action?}
    AC -->|Yes| P
    AC -->|No| AD([End])

    AB --> AD
